<legis-body id="H7175885DD65F4797BF7B06213A3A9D6C" style="OLC"> 
<section id="HA6B4C940FBA741E09A4F1CEDA948C161" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short title</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote>
          <short-title>
            <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Faithful Execution of the Law Act of 2014" proposed="true">Faithful Execution of the Law Act of 2014</cato:entity-ref>
          </short-title>
        </quote>.</text>
    </section> 
<section id="HCD8259187F374908BF16B95E8FFBC0C5" section-type="subsequent-section">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Amendment to <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/28/530D">section 530D</external-xref> of title 28, United States Code</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">
        <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/28/530D/a/1/A">
          <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/28/530D">Section 530D(a)(1)(A)</external-xref> of title 28, United States Code</cato:entity-ref>, is amended—</text> 
<paragraph id="H3B11B7E023474A7DA59864F7A05E0DE6">
        <enum>(1)</enum>
        <text>by inserting <quote>or any other Federal officer</quote> before <quote>establishes or implements a formal or informal policy</quote>; and</text>
      </paragraph> 
<paragraph id="HEA86C88A06EB4D89B0CF949BD1182898">
        <enum>(2)</enum>
        <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/28/530D/a/1/A/i">clause (i)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>on the grounds that such provision is unconstitutional</quote> and inserting <quote>and state the grounds for such policy</quote>.</text>
      </paragraph>
    </section> 
